00:45:10,768 --> 00:45:11,851
Rym: Did you beat all the side quests?

714
00:45:11,871 --> 00:45:12,753
Rym: Did you unlock everything?

715
00:45:12,773 --> 00:45:13,595
Rym: Did you 100% it?

